'''Njinska's Tavern''' was a popular [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located on [[Phyrstal Island]] in the resort city of [[Le Yer]] on the planet [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]]. It was entirely made out of wood and its windows were very large and contained stained-glass art. It had a large T-shaped stage which featured many high quality acts and had a large wide bar along one wall. The stage had a trap door that led to a several meter long angled shaft which ran under the stage and to a back door. The tavern was serviced by three [[Bartender droid/Legends|bartender droids]] and had two large [[Human/Legends|Human]] bouncers for protection.

[[Brinaloy N'Vaari]] was a frequent performer at the tavern.

